122
00:15:05,797 --> 00:15:15,625
To spare a long story short, they had a falling out, a careless remark, wounded Resh Lakish, his lifelong chavruta, so badly

123
00:15:16,265 --> 00:15:24,969
that they fell out, and despite the pleading of Rabbi Yochanan, who was Reish Lakish's wife, caught in the middle of this, they never reconciled.

124
00:15:25,269 --> 00:15:31,231
Reish Lakish got sick and died, and Rabbi Yochanan had to find a new chavruta who was not satisfactory.

125
00:15:32,812 --> 00:15:42,136
